              "type": "stat_block_section"
            },
            "effect": "A target creature within 30 feet must succeed at a DC 25 Will save or gain the effects of cursed metamorphosis, being polymorphed into a pig whose girth is determined by the target's wealth. After 24 hours, the target can end this effect using a Dismiss action, at which point the yeongno becomes aware that the effect has ended. A yeongno can use Fortune's Favor only if no targets are currently under its effects.",
